Package EvolutionaryProgramming

package EvolutionaryProgramming
This package represents an Evolutionary Programming algorithm.

It simulates the process of natural selection, wherein the best-fitted individuals survive. Individuals can also reproduce, mutate, and die. A group of individuals forms a population that can be affected by epidemics.
